      <title>红色浪潮增加达成协议的可能性，债务上限紧张局势有望缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/debt-limit-ructions-seen-easing-as-red-wave-boosts-odds-of-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一些华尔街策略师表示，一个可能统一的美国政府可能会使在财政部借款权限耗尽之前更容易达成暂停或提高债务上限的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/debt-limit-ructions-seen-easing-as-red-wave-boosts-odds-of-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:55:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥比索因莱特希泽将领导美国贸易政策的报告而暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/mexican-peso-slumps-on-report-lighthizer-to-lead-us-trade-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在《金融时报》报道罗伯特·莱特希泽被唐纳德·特朗普新政府任命为美国贸易代表后，墨西哥比索扩大下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/mexican-peso-slumps-on-report-lighthizer-to-lead-us-trade-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:42:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>进口量大幅下降，美国对外国汽油的依赖减弱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/us-dependence-on-foreign-gasoline-weakens-with-imports-plunging</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国是世界上最大的汽油消耗国，历史上一直依赖进口来满足部分需求。现在，随着该国燃料制造商的蓬勃发展，对外国供应的依赖正在迅速下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/us-dependence-on-foreign-gasoline-weakens-with-imports-plunging</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:40:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>艾伯塔省在令人震惊的解雇事件后任命养老金管理公司临时首席执行官</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/alberta-names-interim-ceo-for-pension-manager-after-shock-firing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周四令人震惊地解雇了整个董事会后，阿尔伯塔省政府任命一位长期任职的官僚为该省养老基金管理公司的临时首席执行官。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/alberta-names-interim-ceo-for-pension-manager-after-shock-firing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:38:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>YPF 正与超级巨头就阿根廷液化天然气工厂的股权进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/ypf-in-talks-with-supermajors-for-equity-in-argentina-lng-plant</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷最大的石油和天然气钻探公司、国营的 YPF SA 正在与全球超级巨头进行谈判，希望成为其液化天然气出口项目的股权合作伙伴，而该公司的首席执行官暗示马来西亚国家石油公司可能会退出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/ypf-in-talks-with-supermajors-for-equity-in-argentina-lng-plant</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 17:36:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普胜选提振信贷需求，利差降至 1998 年低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/trump-win-boosts-demand-for-credit-driving-spreads-to-1998-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选、股市飙升以及美联储再次降息之后，投资者纷纷将资金投入美国公司债券，将风险溢价推至25年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/trump-win-boosts-demand-for-credit-driving-spreads-to-1998-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 16:24:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿克曼称阿姆斯特丹暴力事件是除名的临界点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/ackman-seeks-to-remove-pershing-square-s-amsterdam-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁比尔·阿克曼表示，在荷兰发生针对以色列足球迷的暴力事件后，他将寻求将潘兴广场控股有限公司从阿姆斯特丹泛欧交易所的上市名单中移除。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/ackman-seeks-to-remove-pershing-square-s-amsterdam-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 14:44:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊坎企业减半股息以增持 CVR 能源股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/icahn-enterprises-halves-dividend-to-boost-cvr-energy-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁激进投资者卡尔·伊坎 (Carl Icahn) 的投资基金将把股息削减一半，因为其计划增持 CVR Energy Inc. 的股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-08/icahn-enterprises-halves-dividend-to-boost-cvr-energy-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 08 Nov 2024 12:22:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管市场仍维持区间波动，但油价因中国需求低迷而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的刺激措施令投机者失望后，油价下跌，但不足以使价格脱离7月份以来的最窄交易区间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-november-8</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:30:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
